snippet.title: Dead Effect 2 - Official PC & Console Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The official PC and console release trailer for Dead Effect 2.

Dead Effect 2 is coming out on Steam in May 2016, and on PS4 and Xbox One in June 2016.

For more information and the latest news about the game:
